You can use Docker for create local DB for test app
Linux command: 'sudo docker-compose up -d'
Windows command: open power-shell, execute 'docker-compose up -d'

WARNING!!!
Supported only linux containers.

required oracle 1.8 JDK or 1.8 OpneJDK

Linux:
    Run test: 'dradlew test'
    Build project: 'dradlew build'
    Run app: 'java -jar build/libs/xml_test_app-<version_of_app>.jar'

Windows:
    Run test: 'dradlew.bat test'
    Build project: 'dradlew.bat build'
    Run app: 'java -jar build/libs/xml_test_app-<version_of_app>.jar'

Use 'http://localhost:8080' in you web browser for access to web-app